{"tid":709393,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"日本隊武藤嘉紀笑容加朱古力肌融化粉絲","createTime":"2018-06-20T03:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T08:38:53.000Z","uid":161096,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fac02bc186bb2d776c47daad4f1b1eecbb3fc9ee","tid":709393,"uid":161096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:16:19.000Z","msg":"世界盃正式開幕以來，唔係只讓歐美國家滿身肌肉嘅選手專美，亞洲國家日本都有好多球員顏值高到令人尖叫，本屆日本隊最受女粉絲喜愛的，大概就是今年25歲的小鮮肉武藤嘉紀。，佢濃眉大眼，眉宇間帶著自信，笑起來超陽光，直接融化人，鮮肉指數爆燈!<br />\n<br />\n身為日本隊前鋒嘅武藤嘉紀，有著一雙濃眉大眼，帥氣嘅五官擄獲許多女球迷的芳心，佢嘅笑容令唔少粉絲融化，佢唔只多亞洲女粉絲，連小朋友同西洋女fans都鍾意佢。武藤一向予日本人一份乾淨企理感覺，佢一身朱古力腹肌亦鮮肉指數爆標!<br />\n<br />\n不過，武藤已有另一半，而且係大美女，粉絲捶心肝直呼「老天不公平」，佢喺2015年已同空姐女友完婚，據說妻子長相神似日本女星皆藤愛子，日本爆料網都鋪過佢愛妻嘅相，又真係靚女。武藤嘅愛家形象亦十分出名，佢已做咗老竇，長女已於前年4月誕生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2M5azy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2M5azy5&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=59c873b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M5azy5</a>"},{"pid":"a266b2b253302c7fb705c460528f6e86045c38e4","tid":709393,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79eb2cfe896078ea53cefe5faf3de1ca93db021","tid":709393,"uid":18485,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.kininarublog.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/2017-08-12-mainz-yoshinori-muto_um4z0laddtoz1v0lzj8arxcxs.jpg?fit=430%2C230\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.kininarublog.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F2017-08-12-mainz-yoshinori-muto_um4z0laddtoz1v0lzj8arxcxs.jpg%3Ffit%3D430%252C230&h=3afb2b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救樓豬老母"},{"pid":"ac6559592c0a424592eeb330e56ab44f24023bed","tid":709393,"uid":77355,"like":0